{"tid":1637735,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"罷！藍店/中資/奶共企業！（溫故知新）","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T00:50:19.000Z","uid":328342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7aa71f128f04fa6846cfc5f00545b468a05f18","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"首選幫襯中小型黃店，次選誠哥。<br />\n黃藍店大家有哂地圖唔多講～ <br />\n<br />\n想講下<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中資/奶共企業</span></strong>: <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 美心 Maxim's</span></strong><br />\n<strong>List</strong>: (自己溫書) <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2593%2581&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=c4c00f76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81</a><br />\n<strong>Reason</strong>: 大家知，唔多講。留意佢係怡和(Jardines Matheson)旗下牛奶公司國際(Dairy Farm International)嘅子公司。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. M記</span></strong><br />\n<strong>Reason</strong>: 母公司係2017年變咗做「金拱門」，中信股份係最大股東。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 牛奶公司國際其他業務</span></strong><br />\n<strong>List</strong>: 7-11便利店, 萬寧, 惠康超級市場, 宜家家居, Market Place by Jasons, 平記超級市場, Jasons Food &amp; Living, Jasons Ichiba, 3hreeSixty, Oliver's, 民生, , GNC健康食品<br />\n<strong>Reason</strong>: 未FC, 但有傳牛奶公司已向內部發信，要求7-11以後要配合警方予以放行，《蘋果》正向牛奶公司查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n(Source: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190813/59927204?fbclid=IwAR2ZxiywJEpP7s2ek51Ud5xaRpGI517xssP7ocqXVuuvfgk6eGuPGg_JCRM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59927204%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ZxiywJEpP7s2ek51Ud5xaRpGI517xssP7ocqXVuuvfgk6eGuPGg_JCRM&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=2d618316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190813%2F59927204%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ZxiywJEpP7s2ek51Ud5xaRpGI517xssP7ocqXVuuvfgk6eGuPGg_JCRM&h=47b99887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190813/59927204?fbclid=IwAR2ZxiywJEpP7s2ek51Ud5xaRpGI517xssP7ocqXVuuvfgk6eGuPGg_JCRM</a>) <br />\n但睇埋佢Financial Report, Jardines Matheson 2018 年有56%利潤來自大陸(Greater China), 而且未來5年5大發展方向之首就係&quot;Grow In China&quot;, 所以會跪低都唔出奇。<br />\n(Source: <a href=\"https://www.jardines.com/assets/files/Investors/Reports/matheson/jm-ar2018.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jardines.com%2Fassets%2Ffiles%2FInvestors%2FReports%2Fmatheson%2Fjm-ar2018.pdf&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=b3082a0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jardines.com/assets/files/Investors/Reports/matheson/jm-ar2018.pdf</a>)<br />\n(Source: <a href=\"https://insideretail.hk/2019/03/05/dairy-farm-group-ceo-says-restructure-will-take-five-years/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finsideretail.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2Fdairy-farm-group-ceo-says-restructure-will-take-five-years%2F&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=518b40d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://insideretail.hk/2019/03/05/dairy-farm-group-ceo-says-restructure-will-take-five-years/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 四洲集團</span></strong><br />\n<strong>List</strong>: Pokka Cafe, 零食物語, 「四季悅」日本料理, 「功德林」上海素食, 「大阪王將」日式餃子店, 丼吉日本吉列專門店Tonkichi, 魅碗)<br />\n<strong>Reason</strong>: 公司董事會主席係戴德豐 - 「戴先生於2003年至2018年擔任全國政協委員，於此期間由2008年至2018年擔任全國政協常委。彼現在擔任廣東省政協常委。戴先生於2017年獲日本政府頒授「旭日雙光章」，表揚他對日本食品在中國普及化作出的貢獻。彼現時為暨南大學校董，並出任多個社會公職，包括香港食品商會會長、香港友好協進會榮譽會長、港區省級政協委員聯誼會創會主席及香港廣東外商公會主席。」<br />\n(Source: <a href=\"http://www.fourseasgroup.com.hk/hk/aboutus/chairman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fourseasgroup.com.hk%2Fhk%2Faboutus%2Fchairman&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=c11cbc27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.fourseasgroup.com.hk/hk/aboutus/chairman</a>) <br />\n雖然暫時未有跪低嘅事件，但以佢同大陸嘅關係，日後絕對有可能發生，所以都係觀望住，少食為妙。"},{"pid":"449a272466e39e9d5e0cc192cf4c7ff7074777b9","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:31:34.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4cf62c8950bf547bbe36e434a314bc4ba940e88f","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"35501cd143ba8a181dc6ffa4ec506fdbd2793ccd","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"158c282efa8a07adc54e7dcb2dae7408751e0dfc","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"4744ef3b4035d7a805e9dc11bd6333e777a7db76","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:33:36.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"19c445de7e3567ddb89f9c99d41476c0b305bf34","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"96b7be2e269762f69dbd80bb901acb4bde25acd7","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"128c48f6299a43412606371b6dd26c240c51cd1e","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"b2ab2643013fd2dbccfe5c4b12eeb6785de2c3b1","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"36441e8cdcbc03a869fe6c2574843d8d33763273","tid":1637735,"uid":328342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:35:16.000Z","ms